    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Field concerned with the design and creation of productive, low-maintenance agricultural systems and urban environments which have the diversity, stability, and resilience of natural ecosystems.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
